Details:
[+] Configurations and language files' locations can be changed now! View documentation for more info.
[+] You can now run /testnetwork command to see your server's latency with Telegram servers.
[+] We added a warning that shows up when you changes the API Key with /editconf command.
[+] You can now disable the (maybe) annoying startup message.
[+] A help message will show up on console when bot fails to communicate with you.
